document_data.name: House of Wo
document_data.source: [[City of Delights|City of Delights (Gem of Zakhara)]]
document_data.mainbody: The '''House of Wo''' was a [[caravanserai]] located in [[Huzuz]] in [[1367 DR]].{{AQ-time}}
document_data.Description: This four-story structure was capable of lodging hundreds of occupants at the same time, though typically only the cafe was full.
document_data.Activities: Named for its owner, [[Wo]], who was one of the best chefs in the entire city, the House of Wo offered some of the finest dining within the City of Delights.
document_data.Inhabitants: Wo employed [[Fayaniz al-Nokar]] to oversee all non-food-related facets of the House of Wo.
